data.description: Turn Key Primary Home or Income Property!! This turn key ranch home with walkout basement has tons of storage. Home offers 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths and attached 2+ car garage/workshop in The Toqua neighborhood. Walkout lower level has 838 sq ft that is not included in 1708 sq feet total. This home boasts a beautiful front porch which was re-done in 2019, a large back deck accessible from the owners suite and remodeled kitchen area, large remodeled laundry room includes a half bath, private screened porch and irrigation system. Butts up to POA land. Minutes from Toqua and Tanasi golf courses, yacht club, wellness center, rec center, Tugaloo beach/pavilion, walking paths, restaurants, churches, grocery store and so much more.  Come take a look...
